0x59e575 1509 1508 \vCe iti ofera serviciu Raiffeisen Smart Mobile?
  • Consultarea soldurilor
  • Transferuri de bani *
  • Constituire si lichidare depozite *
  • Plata facturilor de utilitati *
  • Localizezi orice bancomat sau agentie Raiffeisen Bank
  • Informatii financiare utile
  • Siguranta maxima!
* disponibil doar clientilor persoane fizice si juridice tip IMM.

Avantaje
  • Activare gratuita
  • Comisioane cu pana la 85% mai mici decat in agentie
  • Disponibilitate:Oricand, oriunde, 24/24, 7/7, chiar si in roaming!
  • Control: Acces permanent la toate conturile tale.
  • Economie de timp:Scapi de drumurile la banca sau la furnizorii de utilitati. Iti rezolvi platile si transferurile in cateva minute fie ca esti in vacanta sau blocat in trafic.
  • Rapiditate: Cateva "touch-uri", si totul este rezolvat!
  • Solutie inteligenta: "Raiffeisen Smart Mobile" este o aplicatie nativa dezvoltata special pentru sistemele de operare Apple & Android si poate fi accesata direct din bowserul de internet al telefonului pentru celelalte telefoane
Cum obtii serviciul Raiffeisen Smart Mobile?
In cazul clientilor persoane fizice serviciul se poate activa in cadrul Raiffeisen Online sau daca nu detii Raiffeisen Online, in orice agentie Raiffeisen Bank . In cazul clientilor de tip persoana juridica serviciul se poate activa doar din cadrul Raiffeisen Online.

0x59eb5b 1465 1464 \vWhat does the Raiffeisen Smart Mobile service offer?
  • Balance display
  • Payments *
  • Opening and closing deposits *
  • Bill payments *
  • Locating ATM's or Raiffeisen Bank branches
  • Financial information
  • Maximum security!
* available only for private individuals and SME legal entities

Advantages
  • Free activation
  • 85% lower commissions than at the branch
  • Availability: Anytime , anywhere, 24/24, 7/7, even in roaming!
  • Control: Permanent access to all your accounts.
  • Time saving: You don't need to go to the bank or to your billers anymore. You can make your payments and transfers in minutes whether you are on vacation or stuck in traffic.
  • Rapiditate: A few touches and everything is done!
  • Smart solution: "Raiffeisen Smart Mobile" is a native application especially developed for Apple & Android operating systems and that can be accessed directly from your phone internet browser for other phone types.
How can you become a Raiffeisen Smart Mobile service client?
If you are a Private Individual, the service can be activated from the Raiffeisen Online application. If you do not own the application, you can activate the service in any Raiffeisen Bank branch. If you are a Legal Entity the service can be activated only from the Raiffeisen Online application.

0x59e575 1509 1508 \vCe iti ofera serviciu Raiffeisen Smart Mobile?
  • Consultarea soldurilor
  • Transferuri de bani *
  • Constituire si lichidare depozite *
  • Plata facturilor de utilitati *
  • Localizezi orice bancomat sau agentie Raiffeisen Bank
  • Informatii financiare utile
  • Siguranta maxima!
* disponibil doar clientilor persoane fizice si juridice tip IMM.

Avantaje
  • Activare gratuita
  • Comisioane cu pana la 85% mai mici decat in agentie
  • Disponibilitate:Oricand, oriunde, 24/24, 7/7, chiar si in roaming!
  • Control: Acces permanent la toate conturile tale.
  • Economie de timp:Scapi de drumurile la banca sau la furnizorii de utilitati. Iti rezolvi platile si transferurile in cateva minute fie ca esti in vacanta sau blocat in trafic.
  • Rapiditate: Cateva "touch-uri", si totul este rezolvat!
  • Solutie inteligenta: "Raiffeisen Smart Mobile" este o aplicatie nativa dezvoltata special pentru sistemele de operare Apple & Android si poate fi accesata direct din bowserul de internet al telefonului pentru celelalte telefoane
Cum obtii serviciul Raiffeisen Smart Mobile?
In cazul clientilor persoane fizice serviciul se poate activa in cadrul Raiffeisen Online sau daca nu detii Raiffeisen Online, in orice agentie Raiffeisen Bank . In cazul clientilor de tip persoana juridica serviciul se poate activa doar din cadrul Raiffeisen Online.

0x59eb5b 1465 1464 \vWhat does the Raiffeisen Smart Mobile service offer?
  • Balance display
  • Payments *
  • Opening and closing deposits *
  • Bill payments *
  • Locating ATM's or Raiffeisen Bank branches
  • Financial information
  • Maximum security!
* available only for private individuals and SME legal entities

Advantages
  • Free activation
  • 85% lower commissions than at the branch
  • Availability: Anytime , anywhere, 24/24, 7/7, even in roaming!
  • Control: Permanent access to all your accounts.
  • Time saving: You don't need to go to the bank or to your billers anymore. You can make your payments and transfers in minutes whether you are on vacation or stuck in traffic.
  • Rapiditate: A few touches and everything is done!
  • Smart solution: "Raiffeisen Smart Mobile" is a native application especially developed for Apple & Android operating systems and that can be accessed directly from your phone internet browser for other phone types.
How can you become a Raiffeisen Smart Mobile service client?
If you are a Private Individual, the service can be activated from the Raiffeisen Online application. If you do not own the application, you can activate the service in any Raiffeisen Bank branch. If you are a Legal Entity the service can be activated only from the Raiffeisen Online application.
